Child killed after fall from truck in Orange County

Rougemont, N.C. â€” Officials in Orange County said a 4-year-old child fell from the back of a Chevy Blazer and was run over Friday afternoon off N.C. Highway 57 between Sawyer and Bunny roads. 
The accident happened just after 3 p.m., and the child died of her injuries. Credits
